ass="classname">PSpell\Dictionary</a></span>  instance now; previously, a <a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="link">resource</a> was expected. </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.pspell-store-replacement-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <span>   <div class="example" id="">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">pspell_store_replacement()</strong></span></strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$pspell_config </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pspell_config_create</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"en"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">pspell_config_personal</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pspell_config</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"/var/dictionaries/custom.pws"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">pspell_config_repl</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pspell_config</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"/var/dictionaries/custom.repl"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pspell </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">pspell_new_config</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pspell_config</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">pspell_store_replacement</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$pspell</s